Criteo Uplift Prediction Dataset — License and Attribution
==========================================================

The file `criteo_uplift_fixture.csv` in this directory is a 3,000-row
deterministic subsample of the Criteo Uplift Prediction Dataset (v2.1),
created for CI smoke tests and adapter validation only.

